item.title: online I-group
item.description: 13:59 Thursday 17 December 2015 JST I group went a little long due to a long 2nd round process for a man who was late to the group after having committed specifically to being on time. I felt anger and realized it stemmed from my desire to be prepared and my desire to procrastinate, which often conflict inside me.

item.title: Next I-group meetings
item.description: 20:51 Friday 23 October 2015 JST Great I-group today, and we have scheduled the next six meetings: 16 November 30 November 14 December 28 December 11 January 25 January I won’t be able to attend on the 25th, but someone will be there. Feeling excited about getting the meetings going again!
